	<section>
		<h1>Plan smarter. Waste less. Sell with confidence.</h1>
		<p>
			Wakefern Marketplace synchronizes household pantry data with local seller forecasts so food gets used at peak freshness
			and stores hit their revenue targets with less spoilage.
		</p>
		<div class="actions">
			<Button href="/buyer/login">Buyer portal</Button>
			<Button href="/seller/login" variant="secondary">Seller dashboard</Button>
