		<p>
			Track what you own, auto-build shopping lists for upcoming events, and receive timely alerts before ingredients expire.
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Unified pantry inventory with expiry insights.</li>
			<li>Event planning that reuses items already on hand.</li>
			<li>Marketplace suggestions tailored to your household.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
	<section>
		<h2>Sellers</h2>
		<p>
			See demand spikes before they hit, optimize restocks, and launch promotions that match local shopper intent.
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Zip-level demand forecasts derived from buyer plans.</li>
			<li>Spoilage risk alerts to protect perishable inventory.</li>
			<li>Promotion tools to capture emerging trends.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
